WEBVTT

01:43.090 --> 01:45.950
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:48.930
[Episode 33]

01:50.270 --> 01:52.190
If there are any chat records

01:52.350 --> 01:53.820
or recordings,

01:53.990 --> 01:55.310
they should be saved on the computer

01:55.380 --> 01:56.229
or on a USB drive.

01:56.350 --> 01:57.240
You didn't find any?

01:57.640 --> 01:59.509
But we've all looked through

01:59.539 --> 02:00.620
Ding Jing's Internet legacy.

02:01.640 --> 02:02.630
We found nothing.

02:04.590 --> 02:05.640
Last time you went there,

02:05.670 --> 02:07.160
Did you see

02:07.230 --> 02:08.830
anything that looks like

02:08.870 --> 02:10.979
a disguised voice recorder

02:11.270 --> 02:12.750
or a USB drive?

02:12.830 --> 02:13.500
No?

02:13.630 --> 02:14.390
No.

02:14.430 --> 02:16.090
The forensic examination was already carried out last time.

02:16.270 --> 02:17.510
Besides, her parents were there that day.

02:17.510 --> 02:18.350
We specifically told them

02:18.390 --> 02:19.530
to contact us immediately

02:19.670 --> 02:20.590
if they found anything.

02:23.470 --> 02:24.500
It can't be.

02:27.280 --> 02:27.829
Let's go there again.

02:29.230 --> 02:30.040
You come with us.

02:30.750 --> 02:31.290
Okay.

02:48.430 --> 02:48.990
Uncle.

02:50.030 --> 02:50.829
We're here.

02:53.630 --> 02:55.450
Jiang, you are here.

02:59.280 --> 03:00.510
You can search

03:01.110 --> 03:02.310
this place as you like.

03:03.380 --> 03:04.640
If necessary,

03:05.350 --> 03:06.430
you can remove

03:07.310 --> 03:10.040
the lights

03:10.990 --> 03:12.150
or the bookcase.

03:13.430 --> 03:14.190
Anyway,

03:14.990 --> 03:16.510
the new owner

03:17.280 --> 03:18.990
will take all these down

03:19.030 --> 03:20.380
and renovate it.

03:23.070 --> 03:24.440
Thank you for your cooperation.

03:24.870 --> 03:25.930
I also hope

03:27.310 --> 03:28.270
I can see the day

03:28.290 --> 03:29.990
the murderer is sentenced.

03:31.030 --> 03:31.890
Looks like

03:33.310 --> 03:34.390
I can't make it in time.

03:36.579 --> 03:37.630
Your aunt

03:38.790 --> 03:39.710
was hospitalized again.

03:42.430 --> 03:43.550
Since Jing…

03:49.270 --> 03:52.310
She completely broke down.

03:54.990 --> 03:56.750
I have to get her out of here as soon as possible.

03:59.030 --> 03:59.880
Don't worry.

04:00.070 --> 04:01.270
We will find out the truth.

04:04.270 --> 04:05.100
Thank you.

04:11.510 --> 04:12.270
I...

04:12.960 --> 04:14.700
I won't disturb your work.

04:15.430 --> 04:16.410
Go ahead.

04:16.829 --> 04:17.310
Okay.

04:27.950 --> 04:28.830
Search carefully.

04:30.710 --> 04:31.770
Don't take apart their cabinet.

04:31.990 --> 04:32.590
Get to work.

04:38.890 --> 04:41.590
[Bay of Horizon, No. 5]

05:18.230 --> 05:18.990
How is it?

05:19.490 --> 05:21.020
This is the only place I haven't searched yet.

05:22.210 --> 05:23.380
I searched the basement.

05:23.470 --> 05:24.150
I didn't find anything.

05:24.710 --> 05:25.550
I think it should be

05:25.550 --> 05:26.800
in her own room.

05:27.350 --> 05:28.240
Look carefully.

05:28.390 --> 05:29.470
Search every corner.

06:04.830 --> 06:05.820
Is this...

06:08.570 --> 06:09.440
a USB driver?

06:12.250 --> 06:17.350
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

06:28.930 --> 06:38.380
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

06:39.510 --> 06:41.320
You sent me that video.

06:41.390 --> 06:42.550
You asked me to force her!

06:42.590 --> 06:43.190
Now that she's dead,

06:43.230 --> 06:44.300
you're also responsible.

06:44.390 --> 06:45.650
We didn't force her to die.

06:45.830 --> 06:47.560
She did it herself.

06:47.630 --> 06:49.060
She committed suicide willingly.

06:49.540 --> 06:50.390
Did you ever

06:50.390 --> 06:51.720
tell her to die?

06:51.909 --> 06:53.370
Of course not.

06:53.400 --> 06:54.480
Then, why are you panicking?

06:53.470 --> 06:59.500
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

06:54.590 --> 06:55.390
I'm just afraid

06:55.430 --> 06:56.840
Coach Zhou will tell on me.

06:56.950 --> 06:57.880
He won't.

06:58.110 --> 06:59.630
The police have asked him about it.

07:00.110 --> 07:01.280
If he dared to say it,

07:01.590 --> 07:02.190
both of us

07:02.190 --> 07:03.190
would have long been taken away.

07:03.310 --> 07:03.830
But now, the police

07:03.870 --> 07:05.820
closed the case with the conclusion of suicide.

07:05.870 --> 07:08.130
It means no one told the truth.

07:08.230 --> 07:09.570
Aren't you going abroad?

07:10.340 --> 07:11.350
Leave as soon as possible.

07:11.750 --> 07:13.360
Don't ever come back.

07:13.710 --> 07:14.310
Only you and I

07:14.350 --> 07:15.660
know this.

07:16.110 --> 07:17.180
If we don't tell anyone,

07:17.510 --> 07:18.890
no one will know.

07:19.070 --> 07:20.680
But even though Coach Zhou hasn't told anyone yet,

07:20.740 --> 07:22.270
it doesn't mean he won't say it in the future.

07:22.630 --> 07:23.640
I'll keep an eye on him

07:23.830 --> 07:24.800
and tell him to shut up.

07:24.920 --> 07:25.680
Ding Jing,

07:26.510 --> 07:28.030
forget about this.

07:28.110 --> 07:29.180
Remember my words.

07:30.110 --> 07:31.770
As long as you don't betray me,

07:32.590 --> 07:34.620
you will be fine.

07:38.270 --> 07:39.210
So,

07:39.750 --> 07:41.940
the person who recorded this video

07:42.470 --> 07:43.110
was Wen Peng.

07:48.390 --> 07:50.430
Ask Zhou Zhicheng to come here tomorrow for an interrogation

07:50.510 --> 07:51.610
and see what he says.

07:52.030 --> 07:52.430
Okay.

07:54.780 --> 07:55.880
It's late today.

07:56.190 --> 07:56.670
Get some rest.

07:56.880 --> 08:01.170
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

08:01.270 --> 08:05.430
[Outpatient]

08:11.950 --> 08:13.330
Here, eat something first.

08:15.660 --> 08:16.950
I'll pass.

08:18.910 --> 08:19.950
We're not in the mood.

08:19.990 --> 08:20.800
Take it away.

08:21.190 --> 08:21.830
Even if you don't want to eat,

08:21.830 --> 08:22.930
our baby needs to eat.

08:23.150 --> 08:23.920
Dr. Lu,

08:25.190 --> 08:25.870
your mom is already showing signs

08:25.870 --> 08:26.970
of independent breathing.

08:27.070 --> 08:28.330
Her basic condition is stable.

08:28.550 --> 08:29.390
She should be able to

08:29.430 --> 08:30.670
be transferred to a general ward tonight.

08:31.030 --> 08:31.920
That's great news.

08:33.070 --> 08:33.870
But she still needs

08:33.870 --> 08:35.000
24-hour care.

08:35.470 --> 08:35.950
Come with me

08:35.950 --> 08:36.740
to handle the paperwork.

08:36.789 --> 08:37.190
Okay.

08:41.880 --> 08:43.480
Finally, there's some good news.

08:43.510 --> 08:44.750
Otherwise, Lu Yan will collapse.

08:45.030 --> 08:46.160
You are going to collapse, too.

08:46.180 --> 08:47.310
Take a bite.

08:49.450 --> 08:50.320
How is it?

08:52.110 --> 08:53.020
How is Auntie?

08:53.790 --> 08:54.780
Her condition is stable.

08:54.830 --> 08:55.390
The doctor said

08:55.430 --> 08:57.000
she could move to a general ward this evening.

09:00.270 --> 09:01.510
You can go back.

09:01.550 --> 09:02.340
I'll stay here to take care of her.

09:03.030 --> 09:04.540
We'll take your shift tomorrow.

09:04.790 --> 09:05.310
Tonight,

09:05.310 --> 09:06.150
I'll leave them to you.

09:06.170 --> 09:07.660
Okay. Don't worry.

09:07.820 --> 09:09.050
Talk with Lu Yan more.

09:09.080 --> 09:09.790
I know.

09:10.790 --> 09:11.830
I'll leave the food here.

09:11.830 --> 09:12.550
Okay.

09:13.600 --> 09:14.320
Honey.

09:15.580 --> 09:16.830
My waist hurts.

09:16.910 --> 09:17.900
I'll give you a massage.

09:34.670 --> 09:35.240
Lu Yan.

09:36.240 --> 09:37.130
I'm here.

09:41.190 --> 09:41.830
Why don't you

09:41.830 --> 09:42.620
go back and rest?

09:42.670 --> 09:43.870
I'll stay here to watch her.

09:46.160 --> 09:47.540
I want to stay with my mom.

09:48.430 --> 09:49.390
I know.

09:50.510 --> 09:52.350
The doctor said,

09:52.660 --> 09:53.430
on one hand,

09:53.470 --> 09:54.810
we have to rely on Auntie's willpower;

09:55.230 --> 09:56.650
♫The day♫

09:55.870 --> 09:56.830
on the other hand,

09:57.270 --> 09:58.830
she needs our care for a long time.

09:57.720 --> 10:00.530
♫You barged into my world♫

09:59.670 --> 10:01.180
If you keep this up,

10:01.750 --> 10:02.710
you'll wear yourself out.

10:01.820 --> 10:03.410
♫I knew there wouldn't be♫

10:02.790 --> 10:03.840
Who's going to take care of Auntie then?

10:04.110 --> 10:04.950
Right?

10:04.130 --> 10:07.530
♫Anyone better than you♫

10:06.960 --> 10:07.790
Go back and have some rest.

10:08.750 --> 10:09.190
Okay?

10:10.460 --> 10:12.150
♫Too bad♫

10:11.270 --> 10:14.010
[Emergency]

10:14.200 --> 10:16.170
♫I have no right to desire in my life♫

10:17.000 --> 10:18.800
♫I missed my chance with you♫

10:20.020 --> 10:23.260
♫Can we blame it on fate?♫

10:25.080 --> 10:27.940
♫Love songs always warn us♫

10:28.580 --> 10:36.020
[Patient Guidelines]

10:28.800 --> 10:31.790
♫Never to believe in forever and ever♫

10:33.560 --> 10:36.700
♫I always go all out; my naivety's to blame♫

10:37.190 --> 10:40.740
♫Bear the pain and heartache♫

10:41.280 --> 10:44.150
♫Your kiss is♫

10:45.520 --> 10:50.470
♫Indelibly tattooed in my heart♫

10:51.190 --> 10:55.000
♫Believing in the rekindling of love♫

10:56.320 --> 10:59.660
♫You're closer than family♫

11:00.290 --> 11:03.710
♫Yet more unfamiliar than strangers♫

11:04.530 --> 11:08.010
♫Risking it all, only to be reciprocated with cruelty♫

11:09.090 --> 11:11.270
♫Aren't I stupid?♫

11:12.200 --> 11:15.480
♫Someone who was once closer than family♫

11:16.420 --> 11:19.960
♫Must I give up my soul?♫

11:20.810 --> 11:27.580
♫I can never love anyone else again♫

11:27.440 --> 11:28.290
You're awake.

11:30.910 --> 11:31.470
Are you hungry?

11:31.870 --> 11:32.850
Do you want to eat something?

11:33.860 --> 11:36.640
♫Love songs always warn us♫

11:37.590 --> 11:40.570
♫Never to believe in forever and ever♫

11:40.150 --> 11:41.180
Go back home to have a rest.

11:41.200 --> 11:42.210
Don't stay here anymore.

11:42.330 --> 11:45.480
♫I always go all out; my naivety's to blame♫

11:43.070 --> 11:43.620
I'm okay.

11:45.980 --> 11:49.520
♫Bear the pain and heartache♫

11:50.060 --> 11:52.880
♫Your kiss is♫

11:52.730 --> 11:53.970
It's warm. Have a sip.

11:54.300 --> 11:59.250
♫Indelibly tattooed in my heart♫

11:59.970 --> 12:03.790
♫Believing in the rekindling of love♫

12:05.110 --> 12:08.420
♫You're closer than family♫

12:08.130 --> 12:08.840
Want some?

12:09.080 --> 12:12.490
♫Yet more unfamiliar than strangers♫

12:13.310 --> 12:16.790
♫Risking it all, only to be reciprocated with cruelty♫

12:16.010 --> 12:16.840
Eat.

12:17.880 --> 12:20.050
♫Aren't I stupid?♫

12:17.990 --> 12:19.270
There's no need to worry about me.

12:20.980 --> 12:24.260
♫Someone who was once closer than family♫

12:21.960 --> 12:23.180
What do you mean?

12:24.430 --> 12:26.030
Just… don't worry.

12:25.210 --> 12:28.740
♫Must I give up my soul?♫

12:29.090 --> 12:30.670
I know you're scared,

12:29.590 --> 12:35.260
♫I can never love anyone else again♫

12:32.120 --> 12:33.710
so you take care of me

12:33.750 --> 12:34.630
and my mom

12:35.230 --> 12:36.360
attentively.

12:35.430 --> 12:38.900
♫Don't fall for the sad eyes♫

12:37.990 --> 12:39.420
But my mom is

12:39.410 --> 12:42.510
♫Don't let fate succeed♫

12:39.630 --> 12:41.200
out of danger.

12:41.430 --> 12:42.390
I can take care of her

12:42.470 --> 12:44.170
and myself.

12:43.040 --> 12:44.830
♫We're all grown ups♫

12:45.710 --> 12:48.740
♫Transformation is a process♫

12:48.190 --> 12:49.370
These days,

12:49.880 --> 12:52.160
♫I'd rather be covered in scars♫

12:53.230 --> 12:55.760
♫Than give up on the possibility of us♫

12:53.550 --> 12:55.630
I've figured a lot of things out.

12:56.760 --> 12:59.980
♫You're closer than family♫

12:58.750 --> 13:00.520
I've come to see that

13:00.520 --> 13:03.470
♫Our love is practically doomed♫

13:00.990 --> 13:01.990
I used to avoid problems

13:02.030 --> 13:03.490
whenever I encountered them.

13:04.290 --> 13:06.610
♫I'm not asking for anything profound♫

13:04.550 --> 13:05.580
I don't like to face them.

13:06.470 --> 13:08.030
I thought without facing them,

13:07.380 --> 13:11.460
♫I just want to love this one person♫

13:09.390 --> 13:10.310
the problems can be solved by themselves.

13:12.240 --> 13:15.810
♫Someone who was once closer than family♫

13:12.390 --> 13:13.350
But this time,

13:15.000 --> 13:16.270
I won't run away anymore.

13:16.710 --> 13:20.240
♫From now on, until the end of time♫

13:19.150 --> 13:20.990
I want to face it together with you.

13:21.670 --> 13:24.990
♫No blood ties, yet more important♫

13:25.990 --> 13:28.690
♫Than family♫

13:29.580 --> 13:30.820
No matter what,

13:30.090 --> 13:34.330
♫The one I lay my heart bare to♫

13:33.430 --> 13:34.470
I will always be with you.

13:35.150 --> 13:39.200
♫My dear stranger♫

13:40.950 --> 13:42.180
Do what you should do.

13:44.750 --> 13:45.550
I'll wait for you here.

14:44.530 --> 14:45.740
Okay, you can stop playing it.

14:50.600 --> 14:51.710
I'll tell you everything.

15:00.840 --> 15:01.940
Three years ago,

15:03.080 --> 15:04.770
I was diagnosed with cancer in the hospital.

15:06.110 --> 15:07.840
The doctor said I could have chemotherapy.

15:10.040 --> 15:11.040
But I knew

15:12.610 --> 15:13.750
chemotherapy would just make me live

15:13.790 --> 15:14.870
a few more years.

15:16.600 --> 15:17.630
My wife's illness

15:19.220 --> 15:20.350
had already cost

15:20.440 --> 15:21.420
all our savings.

15:22.270 --> 15:23.430
I couldn't afford

15:23.470 --> 15:24.530
the chemotherapy.

15:25.270 --> 15:26.700
It's nothing

15:26.720 --> 15:28.140
that I die.

15:28.870 --> 15:29.950
But before I die,

15:31.670 --> 15:33.570
there's something I can't let go.

15:35.430 --> 15:36.430
For example,

15:36.430 --> 15:37.830
my paralyzed wife.

15:39.230 --> 15:40.420
For example,

15:42.910 --> 15:43.970
Deng Man's death.

15:45.950 --> 15:47.150
I might be the last person

15:47.190 --> 15:48.340
in this world who knows

15:48.780 --> 15:49.890
that she was threatened

15:50.350 --> 15:51.350
and bullied to death.

15:54.270 --> 15:56.050
So, I wanted to do something for her

15:57.200 --> 15:58.150
before I die.

15:59.790 --> 16:00.990
That's why I sent an anonymous letter

16:01.030 --> 16:02.310
to the police.

16:03.300 --> 16:04.810
After they received the anonymous letter,

16:06.760 --> 16:08.070
the police reopened

16:08.350 --> 16:09.910
the investigation of Deng Man's case very quickly.

16:11.750 --> 16:13.030
They found me very quickly, too.

16:15.710 --> 16:17.300
But when I arrived at the police station,

16:20.470 --> 16:22.070
I still didn't have the courage

16:22.110 --> 16:23.830
to tell them about the past between Deng Man and me.

16:24.540 --> 16:25.870
Even though I was almost to die,

16:28.870 --> 16:29.710
I was still afraid

16:29.750 --> 16:31.120
that my reputation would be ruined.

16:36.260 --> 16:37.590
At that moment,

16:38.630 --> 16:39.790
Wen Peng found me.

16:59.490 --> 17:00.260
Coach Zhou.

17:04.109 --> 17:04.950
You are?

17:06.550 --> 17:07.609
I'm Wen Peng.

17:08.150 --> 17:09.440
I'm from the Medicine Class of 2012.

17:09.510 --> 17:11.390
I used to play

17:11.430 --> 17:12.270
on your basketball team before.

17:15.069 --> 17:16.280
I remember now.

17:19.460 --> 17:20.369
You are...

17:19.599 --> 17:28.319
[Hospital Medical Equipment Management Policy]

17:23.030 --> 17:23.910
Cancer.

17:24.400 --> 17:25.490
It's the third stage.

17:26.310 --> 17:27.150
God wants me.

17:27.230 --> 17:27.990
I have no choice.

17:30.330 --> 17:31.600
So, how do you plan to treat it?

17:32.590 --> 17:33.190
I'm not going to.

17:34.300 --> 17:36.930
Chemotherapy costs a lot of money.

17:37.480 --> 17:38.540
I don't have that much money.

17:39.870 --> 17:40.890
What about your wife?

17:40.950 --> 17:42.250
Your health condition

17:42.310 --> 17:43.230
has reached this point.

17:43.680 --> 17:51.990
[Hospital Medical Equipment Management Policy]

17:44.190 --> 17:45.050
I don't know.

17:47.830 --> 17:49.400
I've made contact with the welfare center.

17:50.830 --> 17:51.670
I'll just wait for the news.

17:54.940 --> 17:55.840
Coach Zhou.

17:57.590 --> 17:58.490
I can help you.

18:04.830 --> 18:05.660
He said

18:06.630 --> 18:07.750
he could help me.

18:09.070 --> 18:10.110
He said he had

18:10.150 --> 18:11.690
a fund for cancer,

18:12.230 --> 18:13.970
which could provide me funds

18:14.070 --> 18:15.050
to cure my illness.

18:17.740 --> 18:19.620
He took me to see a doctor

18:20.510 --> 18:22.480
and found a nursing home for my wife.

18:22.870 --> 18:24.430
I didn't think much at first.

18:24.780 --> 18:25.830
I just thought

18:25.870 --> 18:26.910
I met a good man.

18:27.110 --> 18:28.300
So, after some interaction,

18:28.430 --> 18:29.520
we became familiar with each other.

18:32.190 --> 18:33.730
I also told him

18:35.890 --> 18:37.170
some of my shameful past.

18:44.630 --> 18:45.610
Thank you.

18:46.870 --> 18:48.070
Thank you, Wen Peng.

18:49.130 --> 18:50.070
However,

18:50.960 --> 18:51.870
this is too much trouble for you.

18:51.910 --> 18:53.170
You have to come here over and over again

18:53.210 --> 18:54.730
with so much cash.

18:54.860 --> 18:55.880
How about

18:55.910 --> 18:57.390
transferring it to my bank card next time?

18:57.430 --> 18:58.570
It'll be more convenient.

18:59.680 --> 19:01.040
It's okay, Coach Zhou.

19:02.590 --> 19:04.030
I have something to ask you.

19:05.310 --> 19:06.130
Go ahead.

19:06.570 --> 19:07.590
A while ago,

19:07.710 --> 19:09.870
the police came to the school to ask about

19:09.890 --> 19:11.150
a girl named Deng Man

19:11.190 --> 19:12.310
who committed suicide by jumping into the lake.

19:12.870 --> 19:13.670
Do you know that?

19:15.650 --> 19:16.190
I...

19:18.030 --> 19:19.970
How did you know about this?

19:22.030 --> 19:22.870
I'm pretty familiar with

19:22.910 --> 19:24.280
a few of the school leaders.

19:24.430 --> 19:26.170
I had dinner with them a few days ago.

19:26.190 --> 19:27.110
They told me about it.

19:28.990 --> 19:30.060
They also said

19:30.550 --> 19:32.110
the police received an anonymous letter,

19:32.190 --> 19:34.340
claiming that Deng Man didn't commit suicide,

19:34.440 --> 19:35.960
but that she was murdered.

19:36.470 --> 19:37.250
However,

19:37.390 --> 19:38.550
the letter didn't make it clear

19:38.670 --> 19:39.610
who the murderer was.

19:45.030 --> 19:46.170
Actually,

19:46.790 --> 19:48.390
I wrote the anonymous letter.

19:51.990 --> 19:53.150
I watched Deng Man

19:53.190 --> 19:54.230
being bullied back then,

19:56.170 --> 19:58.390
but I didn't stop it in time.

19:58.970 --> 20:00.640
Later, that kind of thing happened,

20:01.080 --> 20:02.900
I've always been feeling guilty,

20:03.470 --> 20:04.990
so I wanted to seek justice for her.

20:06.110 --> 20:07.510
But later I thought that

20:07.550 --> 20:09.110
I might get myself into trouble.

20:09.150 --> 20:10.130
So...

20:11.030 --> 20:12.710
Are you afraid that Ding Jing will cause you trouble?

20:17.690 --> 20:19.350
How did you know about Ding Jing?

20:20.110 --> 20:22.180
Deng Man is the person you cheated with during your marriage.

20:22.390 --> 20:23.270
Ding Jing shot a video

20:23.310 --> 20:24.750
of you two being intimate

20:24.790 --> 20:25.970
and threatened you.

20:26.230 --> 20:28.000
You told Deng Man to bear the insult.

20:28.150 --> 20:29.950
In the end, she was forced to die.

20:30.630 --> 20:31.270
Is that so?

20:34.660 --> 20:35.910
Coach Zhou, you know what?

20:36.910 --> 20:37.790
If Ding Jing

20:37.830 --> 20:39.110
knows about this,

20:39.340 --> 20:40.030
with her temper,

20:40.070 --> 20:41.390
she won't let you go.

20:45.350 --> 20:46.480
But don't worry.

20:46.790 --> 20:48.030
I've already

20:48.070 --> 20:49.870
suppressed this matter on her side.

20:50.670 --> 20:51.550
Some things have passed.

20:51.630 --> 20:53.390
Let the past stay in the past.

20:53.750 --> 20:55.400
Even if you tell the truth,

20:55.670 --> 20:57.150
Deng Man won't come back to life.

20:57.440 --> 20:58.590
Maybe it's better

20:58.590 --> 20:59.490
to take this to the grave.

20:59.590 --> 21:00.690
It's good for everyone.

21:00.950 --> 21:01.640
What do you think?

21:04.910 --> 21:05.470
You...

21:07.220 --> 21:08.850
What do you mean?

21:10.950 --> 21:12.090
You don't want

21:12.790 --> 21:14.210
two women to die quietly

21:16.010 --> 21:17.530
because of you, do you?

21:28.910 --> 21:29.830
In the end,

21:31.050 --> 21:33.160
before Jiang Chengyi and Lu Yan

21:33.190 --> 21:34.110
found me,

21:34.650 --> 21:36.130
Wen Peng contacted me.

21:37.210 --> 21:38.820
He taught me a set of phrases,

21:39.150 --> 21:40.740
showing me how to lie to them.

21:41.250 --> 21:42.690
Last time you chased me,

21:42.790 --> 21:44.560
I called him.

21:44.910 --> 21:46.620
He asked someone to crash your car.

21:46.640 --> 21:47.960
I had no choice.

21:49.970 --> 21:51.330
I could only listen to him.

21:53.020 --> 21:54.030
My life and my wife's life

21:54.060 --> 21:55.110
are both in his hands.

22:01.680 --> 22:02.240
Okay.

22:02.840 --> 22:03.710
Zhou Zhicheng.

22:04.350 --> 22:05.930
We've finished the interrogation.

22:05.950 --> 22:07.470
You are suspected of obstructing justice.

22:08.110 --> 22:09.460
We will further verify

22:09.550 --> 22:10.980
your testimony.

22:11.510 --> 22:12.540
During this period,

22:12.710 --> 22:14.020
you have the right to remain silent

22:14.100 --> 22:15.040
or hire an attorney.

22:15.550 --> 22:16.470
We will officially

22:16.510 --> 22:17.600
arrest you

22:17.710 --> 22:18.470
and transfer you to the court.

22:19.790 --> 22:20.510
Also,

22:21.070 --> 22:23.060
you have cancer now.

22:23.590 --> 22:24.350
And your wife can't take care of

22:24.350 --> 22:25.420
herself.

22:25.880 --> 22:27.610
We will explain to the court

22:27.950 --> 22:28.430
so that you

22:29.020 --> 22:30.090
and Lin Chunmei

22:30.860 --> 22:32.270
can receive proper medical care.

22:32.950 --> 22:33.590
Thank you.

22:36.790 --> 22:37.550
Thank you.

22:49.150 --> 22:50.390
I'm finally free.

23:18.630 --> 23:22.030
♫Charging into the world, with you in my backseat♫

23:23.610 --> 23:26.980
♫Pretending not to care even though you're all I care about♫

23:28.830 --> 23:32.240
♫I couldn't tell you for some unknown reason♫

23:33.430 --> 23:38.490
♫That I like you the way you are♫

23:39.310 --> 23:43.680
♫Like raindrops falling, wishing to return to the sky♫

23:44.470 --> 23:48.880
♫As long as I can meet you, I'd gladly endure anything♫

23:49.400 --> 23:53.930
♫Like a shadow quietly guarding its light source♫

23:54.650 --> 23:58.900
♫You keep walking, and I'll walk with you forever♫

23:55.750 --> 23:56.630
You're up?

23:56.990 --> 23:57.760
Come to eat.

24:00.020 --> 24:04.730
♫You're the shooting star I chase with all my might♫

24:02.910 --> 24:04.090
What are you waiting for?

24:05.960 --> 24:10.660
♫I can't hold you, but I can still make a wish♫

24:06.830 --> 24:07.880
I miss you so much.

24:09.020 --> 24:10.510
I'm right here.

24:10.540 --> 24:11.600
Why do you miss me?

24:10.970 --> 24:15.450
♫So precious, so bittersweet♫

24:13.610 --> 24:15.070
Can you

24:15.750 --> 24:17.360
never leave me?

24:16.770 --> 24:21.210
♫Even the wind knows the one I love is you♫

24:19.790 --> 24:20.820
From now on,

24:21.390 --> 24:22.510
I'll always be by your side.

24:21.520 --> 24:25.710
♫You are the shooting star I gaze at and chase♫

24:27.460 --> 24:31.840
♫You saved my lonely heart♫

25:17.050 --> 25:18.330
It's not over yet.

25:19.790 --> 25:20.600
Lu Yan,

25:21.380 --> 25:22.420
I still have a chance.

25:26.160 --> 25:26.930
Wu Di,

25:27.590 --> 25:28.750
the hit-and-run driver

25:28.790 --> 25:30.420
who hit Yuan Li has confessed.

25:30.710 --> 25:31.820
It was you

25:32.310 --> 25:33.270
who ordered him to do that.

25:37.200 --> 25:37.790
Hao,

25:37.820 --> 25:38.650
show him the photo.

25:40.080 --> 25:42.760
This is a screenshot of the surveillance footage

25:42.790 --> 25:43.430
from half an hour

25:43.470 --> 25:44.750
before Yuan Li's incident.

25:45.480 --> 25:47.430
All the details of your deal with him

25:47.470 --> 25:49.730
were shown clearly in the footage.

25:50.470 --> 25:52.070
Go to the corner of Dongli Street

25:52.110 --> 25:53.510
and give this to Qiu Laowu.

25:56.670 --> 25:58.240
Tell him to hit this person.

26:02.130 --> 26:03.280
Remind him to see clearly.

26:06.150 --> 26:06.710
Okay.

26:14.790 --> 26:15.310
Well,

26:15.310 --> 26:16.550
there's something that I don't understand,

26:16.630 --> 26:17.360
Wu Di.

26:18.100 --> 26:20.350
Logically speaking, you've been working

26:20.350 --> 26:21.270
beside the boss for so many years.

26:21.310 --> 26:21.990
I think you should be a person

26:22.020 --> 26:23.830
who pays much attention to details.

26:24.680 --> 26:25.550
But how could you end up

26:25.590 --> 26:26.550
being caught on surveillance?

26:27.350 --> 26:28.110
You shouldn't have been.

26:31.410 --> 26:32.150
Also,

26:33.400 --> 26:34.950
we investigated your company's computer.

26:35.420 --> 26:37.200
It's recorded in detail that

26:37.750 --> 26:40.280
it was you who spread rumors in the game

26:40.390 --> 26:41.220
and incited netizens.

26:43.700 --> 26:44.990
Have you ever thought

26:46.260 --> 26:47.150
why these records

26:47.190 --> 26:47.750
would appear

26:47.790 --> 26:48.910
in your company's computer?

26:51.030 --> 26:52.360
You may not

26:53.090 --> 26:56.490
know the current situation

26:56.540 --> 26:58.230
and the seriousness of the problem.

26:58.470 --> 27:01.260
Just with the Yuan Li incident alone,

27:01.750 --> 27:05.040
you're suspected of intentional murder.

27:06.910 --> 27:08.760
Plus, you spread rumors online

27:09.190 --> 27:10.590
and intentionally crashed a police car

27:10.630 --> 27:12.200
to obstruct our investigation.

27:14.200 --> 27:15.230
Think about

27:15.400 --> 27:17.460
the consequences you'll be facing.

27:24.390 --> 27:25.540
Can't figure it out?

27:26.390 --> 27:27.310
Let me analyze it for you.

27:28.470 --> 27:29.550
There are only two possibilities.

27:30.110 --> 27:30.710
Either

27:31.910 --> 27:33.480
you want to bear everything for Wen Peng

27:34.750 --> 27:35.310
or

27:36.170 --> 27:37.510
Wen Peng wants you

27:38.350 --> 27:39.560
to shoulder everything for him.

27:54.950 --> 27:55.510
Officer,

27:56.710 --> 27:57.600
I have a question.

27:58.770 --> 28:00.270
If I provide you

28:00.270 --> 28:01.390
some clues and criminal evidence,

28:03.390 --> 28:04.850
can I negotiate for a reduced sentence?

28:05.070 --> 28:05.750
It's not up to us

28:05.750 --> 28:06.790
to get the sentence reduced.

28:07.550 --> 28:08.310
We will follow

28:08.350 --> 28:09.360
the legal process as usual.

28:09.520 --> 28:10.760
If the information you provide

28:11.110 --> 28:11.920
is valuable,

28:12.590 --> 28:13.580
we will report it truthfully.

28:21.510 --> 28:22.210
Okay.

28:22.990 --> 28:23.950
I'll tell you everything.

28:24.710 --> 28:25.340
All the things were done

28:25.390 --> 28:26.600
under Wen Peng's instructions!

28:32.560 --> 28:34.170
Actually, I was forced, too.

28:34.710 --> 28:36.270
If I didn't do those things for him,

28:36.310 --> 28:37.230
he would threaten me

28:37.270 --> 28:38.520
and my family.

28:39.150 --> 28:39.670
So,

28:40.870 --> 28:41.750
one thing led to another,

28:41.790 --> 28:42.980
and I ended up making too many mistakes.

28:43.470 --> 28:44.880
Do you have proof that

28:45.270 --> 28:45.790
Wen Peng told you

28:45.830 --> 28:47.150
to do everything?

28:49.630 --> 28:50.160
I...

28:51.070 --> 28:52.410
installed a hidden camera

28:52.830 --> 28:54.610
in my apartment.

28:55.430 --> 28:56.680
It recorded some of my conversations

28:56.710 --> 28:57.820
with Wen Peng.

28:58.350 --> 28:59.690
You can check it.

29:00.510 --> 29:01.270
Also,

29:02.830 --> 29:03.910
before Wen Peng left,

29:03.990 --> 29:05.230
he told me to do one thing.

29:06.640 --> 29:07.780
He asked me to make an appointment

29:07.780 --> 29:08.710
with a second-hand car dealer.

29:10.390 --> 29:11.150
I guess

29:12.350 --> 29:14.050
he wanted to buy a car to run away.

29:20.680 --> 29:26.240
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

29:20.990 --> 29:22.510
I don't understand.

29:22.720 --> 29:23.510
If he wanted to flee,

29:23.540 --> 29:24.200
there were many ways to do it.

29:24.660 --> 29:25.190
Why did he have to

29:25.240 --> 29:26.190
buy a used car?

29:28.820 --> 29:30.410
Now that there's a clue, let's just investigate it.

29:30.990 --> 29:33.270
Go to the second-hand car market

29:33.720 --> 29:35.030
and find out which salesperson it was.

29:35.190 --> 29:36.140
Check what car it was,

29:36.310 --> 29:37.930
the model,

29:37.980 --> 29:38.670
whether it had a license plate,

29:38.750 --> 29:39.430
and what the plate number is.

29:39.450 --> 29:40.160
Make it clear.

29:40.900 --> 29:41.770
Yiming.

29:42.060 --> 29:43.130
We'll get going, then.

29:46.710 --> 29:47.570
Sihan,

29:47.720 --> 29:49.920
go to Wu Di's place

29:50.510 --> 29:52.190
and see if the surveillance camera he mentioned

29:52.230 --> 29:53.350
is true.

29:54.110 --> 29:54.780
Yes.

29:55.080 --> 29:55.670
Li Yong.

29:56.280 --> 29:57.150
Let's go.

30:02.350 --> 30:03.950
Are you buying a car or selling a car?

30:04.010 --> 30:04.550
Hello, boss.

30:04.550 --> 30:05.110
We're from the Criminal Investigation Unit

30:05.160 --> 30:05.710
of the Anshan District.

30:05.710 --> 30:07.130
I have a favor to ask you.

30:07.400 --> 30:08.370
Here, take a look at the photo.

30:12.390 --> 30:13.340
He did buy a car

30:13.340 --> 30:14.440
from me.

30:14.830 --> 30:15.350
What car?

30:15.420 --> 30:16.110
What's the plate number?

30:16.770 --> 30:17.540
Hold on.

30:17.590 --> 30:18.510
Let me check it for you.

30:22.400 --> 30:23.680
A black jeep.

30:23.740 --> 30:25.840
PuA3A284.

30:26.230 --> 30:27.190
Do you have the CCTV footage from that day?

30:27.190 --> 30:27.990
Show me.

30:28.020 --> 30:28.780
Yes.

30:45.170 --> 30:46.110
Yue.

30:46.350 --> 30:47.250
That is the car.

30:47.970 --> 30:49.920
-Yes, that's it.
-Thank you, boss. Let's go.

30:57.990 --> 30:58.390
Okay.

30:59.350 --> 31:00.000
Okay.

31:01.200 --> 31:07.080
[Surveillance Network Coverage Areas, Anshan District, Ninghai]

31:02.550 --> 31:03.300
Captain Jiang.

31:03.510 --> 31:04.510
Sihan said he saw

31:04.510 --> 31:05.390
the camera Wu Di mentioned.

31:05.510 --> 31:06.430
He is on his way back now.

31:07.540 --> 31:08.170
Okay.

31:12.840 --> 31:13.790
Hello, Qin Yue.

31:14.190 --> 31:15.190
Hello, Senior.

31:15.340 --> 31:16.670
We found Wen Peng

31:16.710 --> 31:17.770
in the second-hand car market.

31:17.910 --> 31:18.990
He's still there?

31:19.190 --> 31:19.860
Yes.

31:19.990 --> 31:20.950
I guess he has been hiding

31:20.990 --> 31:22.550
in the second-hand car market the whole time.

31:22.870 --> 31:24.130
He's heading in the direction

31:24.190 --> 31:26.620
of Wenchang Village and Baihua Road.

31:26.710 --> 31:27.190
Okay.

31:28.390 --> 31:29.560
Follow him.

31:29.900 --> 31:30.910
Don't expose yourselves.

31:32.470 --> 31:33.640
Report to me if anything happens.

31:33.800 --> 31:35.000
Don't be impulsive.

31:35.470 --> 31:36.110
Just follow him.

31:36.350 --> 31:36.980
Yes.

31:37.200 --> 31:37.710
Okay.

31:44.750 --> 31:52.470
[Surveillance Network Coverage Areas, Anshan District, Ninghai]

31:45.430 --> 31:46.110
Liu Hao.

31:48.550 --> 31:50.130
Buying a used car

31:50.870 --> 31:52.150
and handling the paperwork—

31:52.710 --> 31:53.590
shouldn't it take at most half a day

31:53.590 --> 31:54.270
to get it all done?

31:54.790 --> 31:55.350
Yes.

31:56.390 --> 31:57.910
But Wen Peng is still there.

31:58.550 --> 31:59.260
Why?

32:00.350 --> 32:01.680
If he was ready

32:01.710 --> 32:03.310
to sell Wu Di out,

32:04.350 --> 32:05.890
why did he ask Wu Di to do this?

32:07.710 --> 32:09.050
Now that he has bought the car,

32:09.590 --> 32:10.650
he's still there.

32:11.230 --> 32:12.110
Was he waiting for us?

32:16.370 --> 32:17.890
Did he deliberately expose himself?

32:20.740 --> 32:21.680
Tell Qin Yue

32:21.710 --> 32:22.940
not to act rashly.

32:23.230 --> 32:24.140
Call someone. Let's go over there.

32:24.170 --> 32:24.950
-Let's go.
-Okay.

33:20.260 --> 33:21.040
Yue.

33:21.060 --> 33:22.030
What should we do now?

33:22.370 --> 33:23.150
Wait for a while.

33:23.190 --> 33:24.840
Senior and the others are on their way here.

34:06.870 --> 34:07.510
Yue.

34:07.590 --> 34:08.790
It's been ten minutes.

34:08.860 --> 34:10.330
This place is huge.

34:10.360 --> 34:12.239
What if Wen Peng runs away?

34:16.520 --> 34:17.969
Let's follow him first.

34:39.489 --> 34:40.280
Yue.

34:41.179 --> 34:42.179
Wen Peng's car.

41:54.670 --> 41:55.310
Qin Yue!

41:56.790 --> 41:57.470
Senior.

41:59.190 --> 42:00.110
Senior!

42:11.020 --> 42:11.890
Qin Yue!

42:12.650 --> 42:13.460
Qin Yue!

42:13.770 --> 42:15.120
Senior, don't come in.

42:15.270 --> 42:15.910
There's too much dust.

42:15.950 --> 42:17.420
It might explode.

42:21.990 --> 42:22.840
Senior, go!

42:22.910 --> 42:23.870
It will explode.

42:25.600 --> 42:26.230
Leave me alone.

42:26.270 --> 42:28.160
It will explode here, Senior.

42:32.310 --> 42:34.070
You go first. It will explode!

42:34.150 --> 42:34.830
Senior!
